[6.212, "o", "\u001b[90m\u23fa CLAUDE.local.md \u2014 \"firm is active in this repo\" \u00b7 Profile: rails_app / minitest\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.912, "o", "\u001b[36m\u23fa Task\u001b[0m(engineering-rails:\u001b[97mconvention-reviewer\u001b[0m \u2014 seam A6, reads the Profile)\r\n"]
[7.612, "o", "\u001b[36m\u23fa Bash\u001b[0m(.firm/hooks/firm-gate.sh --report)\r\n"]
[8.612, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.962, "o", "\u001b[91mthe gate would reject this push \u2014 4 un-waived finding(s):\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.312, "o", "  2  \u001b[33mhatch-lock\u001b[0m     inflections.rb, legacy_order.rb  \u001b[90m(silent escape hatches)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.662, "o", "  2  \u001b[33mrest-shape\u001b[0m     routes.rb:6, routes.rb:16       \u001b[90m(verb routes off the 7 actions)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.012, "o", "\u001b[90m  (tdd-private-probe: already waived in the ledger \u2014 won't block)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.562, "o", "the reviewer's dossier goes \u001b[97mbeyond what the cops catch\u001b[0m:\r\n"]
[12.562, "o", "\r\n"]
[13.162, "o", "  1. \u001b[91mHIGH\u001b[0m  the repo's one test file doesn't pass \u2014 it \u001b[91merrors\u001b[0m (2 errors, 0 assertions):\r\n"]
[13.762, "o", "         no work_items migration, and it stubs a method that \u001b[97mdoesn't exist\u001b[0m.\r\n"]
[14.362, "o", "         \u001b[90m\"a test file exists\" was standing in for \"tests pass\" \u2014 it isn't.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.962, "o", "  2. \u001b[91mHIGH\u001b[0m  a genuine internal mock slips past the gate \u001b[91msilently\u001b[0m:\r\n"]
[15.562, "o", "         tdd-internal-mock only speaks RSpec \u2014 this repo is Minitest.\r\n"]
[16.162, "o", "         \u001b[33m\u2192 escalated as a firm gap, not just your code.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[16.762, "o", "  3. \u001b[33mMED \u001b[0m  OrdersController#approve_now is a verb pretending to be a resource.\r\n"]
[17.362, "o", "\r\n"]
[17.962, "o", "  \u001b[90mhonesty check: rest-shape on routes.rb:6 is the stock rails/health route \u2014\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.562, "o", "  \u001b[90ma false positive. ledger it with a reason; don't delete a framework default.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[21.712, "o", "your options: \u001b[97mfix the 3 real ones\u001b[0m, or record a reasoned exception:\r\n"]
[22.262, "o", "  \u001b[36mFIRM_OVERRIDE=\"<rule>@<file>: <reason>\" git push\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[23.362, "o", "\u001b[36mwork-tracker\u001b[0m\u001b[32m \u276f \u001b[0m"]
[23.762, "o", "\u001b[92m# the judgement layer: agents that read your Profile, grade their findings,\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[23.762, "o", "\u001b[36mwork-tracker\u001b[0m\u001b[32m \u276f \u001b[0m"]
[23.912, "o", "\u001b[92m# and catch what the deterministic layer can't \u2014 including firm's own gaps.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
